des:
Over 100 truly terrible Christmas Jokes. If you're in need of a laugh, or just fancy hearing some painful Christmas jokes then use this skill. Get in the festive spirit by using this skill!

- Over 100+ jokes
- Updated regularly
- Great for the whole family

Please use the following example phrases when using Christmas Jokes:
“Alexa, please open Christmas Jokes and tell me a joke”
“Alexa, launch Christmas Jokes”
“Alexa, play Christmas Jokes”
“Alexa, open Christmas Jokes”

If you would like to inform me about how terrible these jokes are you can find me on twitter:
https://twitter.com/VikingSkullApps
